When it finally arrived this time (in parts, my partner was almost finished with his, when mine came) it wasn't quite how we wanted it. My bread was burned, his poached eggs were rock-hard. The server gave the cooks a good talking to in the kitchen, which we could witness from our table. Afterwards he slammed stuff around and started piling up full plates on top of each other under the heater. Having worked as a chef myself I was shocked to see that.
